Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.07,0:07:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an4\fs150\fsp13\fn@思源黑体 medium\bord3.5\b1\c&H3A4829&\3c&HFFFDFE&\frz270\2c&H00FFFF&\2a&HFF&\clip(18.67,82,274.67,98)\t(0,397,\clip(19.2,80,88.8,284.8))\t(1023,1941,\clip(19.2,80,88.8,580))\pos(72,84.77)}观察{\fn@Source Han Sans medium}？{\fn@思源黑体 medium} 观察什么{\fn@Source Han Sans medium}？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.18,0:07:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 你说二号街的超市吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.10,0:07:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,她想做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.00,0:07:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,特工之间应该避免不必要的接触
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.87,0:08:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an4\fs150\fsp13\fn@思源黑体 medium\bord4\b1\c&HC58DB2&\3c&HFFFDFE&\frz270\2c&H00FFFF&\clip(827,165,920,190)\2a&HFF&\pos(875,173)\t(0,898,\clip(827,165,920,436))}黄昏前辈
