Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.92,0:08:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an4\fs150\fsp13\fn@思源黑体 medium\bord4\b1\c&HC78CB2&\3c&HFFFDFE&\frz270\clip(624.95,166.77,698.91,190)\2c&H00FFFF&\2a&HFF&\pos(665,173)\t(0,1601,\clip(624.95,166.77,698.91,564.36))}必需事项吗{\fn@Source Han Sans medium}？
