Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.40,0:08:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊 我也去买一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.26,0:08:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an4\fs150\fsp13\fn@思源黑体 medium\bord3.5\b1\c&HC78CB2&\3c&HFFFDFE&\frz270\2c&H00FFFF&\2a&HFF&\pos(1511.57,96)\clip(1474,88,1546,102)\t(0,2518,\clip(1474,88,1546,940))}杂活不应该交给这个女人来做吗{\fn@Source Han Sans medium}？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.13,0:08:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an4\fs150\fsp13\fn@思源黑体 medium\bord3.5\b1\c&HC78CB2&\3c&HFFFDFE&\frz270\2c&H00FFFF&\2a&HFF&\clip(1395.56,90.67,1454.22,108)\t(0,1525,\clip(1395.56,90.67,1454.22,539.56))\pos(1436.66,96)}难道她不配合吗{\fn@Source Han Sans medium}？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.48,0:08:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,南瓜和意面也很便宜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.01,0:08:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,就是收银要排很长的队
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.72,0:08:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,那家店的虾很不错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.01,0:08:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an4\fs85\fsp13\fn@思源黑体 medium\bord4\b1\c&H3A482B&\3c&HFFFDFE&\frz270\2c&H00FFFF&\2a&HFF&\clip(1620.8,212.8,1724.8,235)\t(0,1607,\clip(1620.8,212.8,1724.8,836.8))\pos(1691.667,608)}{\fs150\fn@Source Han Sans medium}？
